      .threats
        .inner
          .threats-top
            h2.threats-header Stay Ahead of Threats with a Technologically Unique Solution
            .threats-text Acronis is the only backup solution on the market that ensures complete cyber protection. Our team of experts incorporates new-generation technologies that deliver a more robust, battle-tested approach to data protection. This ensures Acronis users enjoy practically zero downtime and fast, reliable recoveries.
          .threats-slider
            .threats-items
              .threats-item
                .threats-image
                  img(src="img/threats1.png" width="276")
                .threats-title Proactive Ransomware Protection
                .threats-caption Acronis Active Protection uses artificial intelligence to distinguish suspicious activity from normal processes. It detects, stops and deflects an attack, protecting files from unauthorized encryption or alteration. Any files impacted are automatically restored.
              .threats-item
                .threats-image
                  img(src="img/threats2.png" width="256")
                .threats-title Blockchain Notarization 
                .threats-caption Acronis Notary is a blockchain-based notary and electronic signature tool that ensures the integrity of files. It validates backups by computing a cryptographic hash that is unique to each file. With this built-in technology, there’s no doubt data is authentic. 
              .threats-item
                .threats-image
                  img(src="img/threats3.png" width="352")
                .threats-title Secure Cyber Protection
                .threats-caption Acronis ensures end-to-end data protection that’s developed by a team of security experts who use a SDLC approach. Data security is at the core of their efforts, at every stage – resulting in 20 security-related patents and over 100 more for data protection.
              
